category: Net
requires: libavahi-glib1 libavahi-common-devel libglib2.0-devel
external-source: avahi
sdesc: "mDNS/DNS-SD/Zeroconf implementation (GLib libdevel)"
ldesc: "Avahi is a system which facilitates service discovery on a local 
network via the mDNS/DNS-SD protocol suite. This enables you to plug 
your laptop or computer into a network and instantly be able to view 
other people who you can chat with, find printers to print to or find 
files being shared."
